com.example.parkinggarage.model.users

Class Manager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.parkinggarage.model.users.User
      • com.example.parkinggarage.model.users.Attendant
        • com.example.parkinggarage.model.users.Manager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Manager
extends Attendant
    The Manager class is a subclass of the User class and the Attendant class. A manager has the ability to create attendants as well as the abilities of an Attendant. This will be used upon the arrival of an attendant to the parking garage.
